<div class="home-page-header">
    <h1 class="animated zoom-in hero-text">Powerful design across all devices</h1>
</div>
<div class="container hidden-overflow"><div class="flex-space-between-except-mobile flex-wrap">
  <div class="animated fade-in-left width-50-percent padded mobile-order-2">
    Bullfrog Websites is a web design and development company located in Meadville, PA. I create responsive websites and web applications for local businesses.
  </div>
  <div class="animated-parent"><div class="animated-child fade-in-down mobile-order-1"><%= image_tag 'location.svg', class: "display-image padded", alt: "location marker" %></div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="container hidden-overflow"><div class="flex-space-between-except-mobile flex-wrap">
  <div class="animated fade-in-left"><%= image_tag 'search.svg', class: "display-image padded", alt: "magnifying glass" %></div>
  <div class="animated fade-in-right width-50-percent padded">
    Most people search online before deciding where to buy. This means your website is often a person's first impression of your business. I can make you a website that will maximize the amount of viewers who choose your business.
  </div>
</div></div>
<h1 class="color1-bg">
  <div class="container"><div class="padded">1-up the competition. Make sure your website is:</div></div>
</h1>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row padded-row flex-grow flex-center">
    <div class="flex-center flex-stretcher flex-wrap">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="icon"><%= image_tag 'maintainable1.svg', alt: "clock" %></div>
        <h1 class="center">Maintainable</h1>
        Having a web designer maintain all your website's information can be expensive. Manage content yourself through a CMS with an easy to use interface.
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="icon"><%= image_tag 'responsive1.svg', alt: "mobile phone and desktop computer" %></div>
        <h1 class="center">Responsive</h1>
        Half of internet users are on a mobile device. It is critical for your website to function just as well on mobile devices as it does on desktops.
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="icon"><%= image_tag 'appealing1.svg', alt: "rose" %></div>
        <h1 class="center">Appealing</h1>
        Keep your customers on your website by making sure it's nice to look at.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<h1 class="color1-bg">
  <div class="container"><div class="padded">Launch your web application.</div></div>
</h1>
<div class="container hidden-overflow"><div class="flex-space-between-except-mobile flex-wrap">
  <div class="animated fade-in-left width-50-percent padded mobile-order-2">
    If you need a website with dynamic, interactive features such as an online web store, a typical designer wouldn't be able to help you. However, I am a web developer as well as designer. I can add any dynamic features your business requires.
  </div>
  <div class="animated-parent"><div class="animated-child fade-in-up mobile-order-1"><%= image_tag 'rocket.svg', class: "display-image padded", alt: "rocket" %></div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="dark-bg-content"><div class="container">
  <div class="center padded">
    <h1 class="color1-bright bold-header">Interested?</h1>
    <a href="<%= contact_path %>" class="colored-call-to-action-btn">Get a quote</a>
    <br><br>
    <h1 class="grey-light bold-header">Still not sure?</h1>
    <a href="<%= work_path %>" class="light-grey-call-to-action-btn">View my past work</a>
  </div>
</div></div>